[src:scikit-image/corner-detection] The performance of the evolved operators has been confirmed experimentally using training and testing sequences of progressively transformed images.
[src:scikit-image/corner-detection] Hence, the proposed GP algorithm is considered to be human-competitive for the problem of interest point detection.
